oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bill Monroe Job No. 17942
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Typed invoice for an order placed by Bill Monroe for 200 two color jumbos announcing The Stella Parton Show on July 31, The Jackie Ward Show on August 1, Carl Perkins on August 7 and 8, Marty Robbins on August 15, Elmer Fudpucker on August 21, Sheb Wooley on August 22, and the Gospel Show on August 28 and 29 at the Brown County Jamboree. Receipt indicates agreed price, size, order quantity, shipping location and description.
